# Zed Agent Rules for lyahelia.art

This is a static GitHub Pages website.

## Start / Preview

Never open `index.html` directly.
Never use `file://`.
Never say this site can be opened directly without a server.

To preview the site, run this from the repository root:

```sh
python3 -m http.server 5173 --bind 127.0.0.1
```

Then open this URL:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:5173
```

In Zed, prefer the project task named:

```text
Start site
```

## Project Shape

- Static HTML/CSS/JS site.
- No npm install is needed.
- No React/Vite/build step is needed.
- Main files: `index.html`, `css/style.css`, `js/main.js`, `pages/`, `images/`, `video/`.

## Editing

- Keep edits focused.
- Do not auto-format unrelated HTML/CSS.
- Preserve existing URLs, image paths, and page paths unless explicitly asked.
